# Notes:
# - Raw data (retail_sales_2025.*) IS tracked as the source of truth.
# - clean/ and charts/ are tracked as deliverables (reproducible via scripts/).
#   If you'd rather regenerate them and keep them out of git, uncomment:
# clean/
# charts/
# - retail.db is ignored (regenerate with: python scripts/load_sqlite.py).
